The paper deals with robot navigation, which is a core topic in robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method uses deep learning techniques to process visual information (cs.CV) and learn a policy for navigation (cs.LG). The approach involves model predictive control (MPC), which is a popular optimization-based technique in control theory and robotics (cs.SY). Finally, the paper also involves some level of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in terms of learning a policy for navigation.
